se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.model

Class SimpleArtifact

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.jguru.nazgul.core.persistence.model.NazgulEntity
      • se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.model.SimpleArtifact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<SimpleArtifact>, se.jguru.nazgul.tools.validation.api.Validatable

    @Entity
public class SimpleArtifact
extends NazgulEntity
implements Comparable<SimpleArtifact>
    Maven artifact data holder, unencumbered by all the dependencies of the Maven core. This class does not contain all the mechanics of the Maven core, implying that the user must take care not to inject insane values (for groupId, artifactId, type etc.).
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
    See Also:
